title: Lambda Handlers — Pipeline Diagram
layout: layout.liquid
---

{% include "lambda-stage-data" %}


<h1 class="font-merriweather text-3xl font-bold mb-6">
  <span class="text-lg font-normal text-gray-60 block">Lambda Handlers</span>
  Pipeline roles & diagram
</h1>

<p class="text-gray-60 mb-8 prose">Role badges shown under <a href="/reference/lambda/code/">Lambda > Function Reference</a> and in the diagram.</p>

<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-8">
  {% for role in roleColors %}
    {% assign idx = 0 %}
    {% for r in roleColors %}
      {% if r == role %}{% assign roleIdx = idx %}{% endif %}
      {% assign idx = idx | plus: 1 %}
    {% endfor %}
    <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full
      {% if roleIdx == 0 %}bg-blue-100 text-blue-800
      {% elsif roleIdx == 1 %}bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-800
      {% elsif roleIdx == 2 %}bg-teal-100 text-teal-800
      {% elsif roleIdx == 3 %}bg-green-100 text-green-800
      {% elsif roleIdx == 4 %}bg-orange-100 text-orange-800
      {% elsif roleIdx == 5 %}bg-red-100 text-red-800
      {% elsif roleIdx == 6 %}bg-purple-100 text-purple-800
      {% endif %}">
      {{ role }}
    </span>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<h2 class="font-merriweather text-xl font-bold mb-4">Pipeline Diagram</h2>

<p class="text-gray-60 mb-8">End-to-end processing flow through the Lambda stages.</p>

<div class="bg-gray-2 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8 overflow-x-auto not-prose">
  <pre class="text-sm leading-relaxed font-mono">
             +-------------+                    +-----------------------------------------+
             |  SQS Event  |        +----------->   Configuration Loading                 |
      +------+  (Trigger)  |        |           |      (Configuration)                    |
      |      +-------------+        |           | `read_rsg_cg_mapping_file` →            |
      |    +------------------+     |           |     `read_current_version` →            |
      +---->      Entry       |     |           |         `read_configuration_file` →     |
           |    (Handler)     |     |           |             `load_active_configuration` |
+----------+ `lambda_handler` |     |           +--+--------------------------------------+
|          +------------------+     |              |
| +---------------------------------+-----+        |  +------------------------------+
| |         S3 Retrieval                  |        |  |   Refinement Pipeline        |
+->           (S3 I/O)                    |        +-->     (Orchestrator)           +-----+
  |  `extract_persistence_id` →           |           | `run_refinement` →           |     |
  |      `get_s3_object_content` →        |           |     `process_jurisdiction` → |     |
  |           `parse_s3_content_to_dict`  |           |         `process_condition`  |     |
  +---------------------------------------+           +------------------------------+     |
                                                                                           |                   |
                                                        +---------------------------+      |
                       +--------------------------------+    Output Writing         <------+
                       |                                |       (Output)            |
                     +-v----------------------+         | `write_refined_outputs` → |
                     |   `RefinerComplete`    |         |     `write_remainder_rrs` |
                     |  Manifest → AIMS (S3)  |         +---------------------------+
                     +------------------------+
  </pre>
</div>
